public GraphModel.GHitDetectResult hitDetect(java.awt.geom.Point2D point)
Given the current drawing of the graph and a point on the grid, this function detects whether or not the point lies on any objects in the drawing. Performance need not be optimal; graphs should be small and frequency is limited by the user.
